      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for something that's been truly loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
