    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the iconic 3.6L M96 flat-six engine paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This wide-body 996.2 variant maintains impeccable mechanical integrity, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a dry undercarriage with zero seepage. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, providing telepathic turn-in, while the Bosch Motronic DME report confirms an over-rev-free history. Finished in a flawless deep-gloss coat with a pristine interior, this example delivers the visceral, naturally aspirated performance and hydraulic steering feedback that defines the era. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
