    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat with a mirror-like clarity, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly with a crisp, tactile response. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its maintenance with an open-checkbook approach. It delivers a driving experience that is as tight, quiet, and responsive as the day it was first delivered. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
